column5: Well with the cold temps it's maken ice again on the River found 3 to 4" in most areas checked ...ice should be in great shape by the weekend ...water is murky and flowing so if your not a die hard with out a floater suite i would give it a few days ...   I placed one hut out to try tonight ....
Woooooo, 3 wheeler! hahaha. i wouldn't trust 3-4"  but thats just me.
